snippet.title: Sonic the Hedgehog x Samba De Amigo - Collaboration Trailer | Sonic Central 2023
snippet.description: Classic Sonic tracks from Sonic Adventure 2 and Sonic Forces will be available to play in Samba de Amigo. Watch the latest trailer for the upcoming rhythm game ahead of its launch on Nintendo Switch on August 29. It will also be available on Meta Quest at a later date.
